[31m-                  15%        9.4%                                                     15%[m
[31m-                  10%                                                                 10%[m
[31m-                   5%                                                          0.0%   5%         0.0%        1.5%[m
[31m-                   0%                                                                 0%[m
[31m-                          Project is               Project is           Project is            Project is              Project is        Project is[m
